<paragraph id="7A0AC81D23783A7986E5BF9787449DC4" blockId="41.[211,1171,438,495]" pageId="41" pageNumber="2479">
Autonomous region in 
<collectingRegion id="B87106FF23783A7987D7BF9787F89DE4" box="[481,676,438,462]" country="China" name="Xinjiang Uygur" pageId="41" pageNumber="2479">Xinjiang Uyghur</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="02A2888D23783A798484BF9787A69DE4" box="[690,762,438,462]" name="China" pageId="41" pageNumber="2479">China</collectingCountry>
, the most northeastern distribution range of 
<taxonomicName id="BDB5B39E23783A798701BFF687449DC4" box="[311,536,470,494]" class="Arachnida" family="Sparassidae" genus="Eusparassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="41" pageNumber="2479" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis id="48C1140F23783A798701BFF684E19DC4" box="[311,445,471,494]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="2479">Eusparassus</emphasis>
species.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
